    (Chaotic)"],["4","Selfless. I use my position to help the downtrodden avoid persecution
    from the authorities. (Good)"],["5","Patriotic. I am a loyal supporter of Phlan
    and its leaders, and see my role as a solemn duty and necessary evil to prevent
    anarchy. (Lawful)"],["6","Manipulative. I use my knowledge to blackmail and manipulate
    others to my own benefit. (Evil)"]]},{"type":"table","colLabels":["d6","Bond"],"colStyles":["col-1
    text-center","col-11"],"rows":[["1","I was framed for a crime I did not commit,
    and seek to bring the true culprit to justice."],["2","I am a part of an underground
    network that smuggles innocent civilians out of the city prior to being raided
    by the authorities."],["3","I miss the glory days of Phlan, before the coming
